      "role": "user",
      "content": "right, but if the \"institutional gatekeeping\" you mentioned is what decides who gets published or hired, then doesn't that mean the system is basically saying that people who use AAVE are inherently less capable of logic or high-level thought, even if they aren't? like, if we keep saying Text A is \"rigorous\" and Text B is \"lacking preparation,\" aren't we just reinforcing the idea that Black cultural speech patterns are incompatible with being smart or professional?",
